<h2 class="mb-4">About SunNext</h2>

<p>
    <strong>SunNext</strong> is a B2B web platform designed for owners and operators of solar parks and energy storage systems. Our goal is to empower clean energy professionals with real-time monitoring, intelligent automation, and market trading insights.
</p>

<h4 class="mt-4">Key Technologies</h4>
<ul>
    <li>ASP.NET Core 8.0 MVC</li>
    <li>Entity Framework Core + SQL Server</li>
    <li>Chart.js + SignalR (optional)</li>
    <li>ASP.NET Identity with Roles</li>
</ul>

<h4 class="mt-4">Use Cases</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Real-time monitoring of solar assets</li>
    <li>Battery optimization and health tracking</li>
    <li>IBEX trading automation with AI guidance</li>
</ul>